(7215, 'Letrozol 2.5 mg 30 f.c.tabs.', 'ليتروزول 2.5مجم 30 قرص', '740', '964', 'Letrozole', 'Synthon hispania', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'لعلاج العقم وحالات تأخر الحمل والانجاب', 'Non-steroidal aromatase inhibitor. infertility', '2.5 mg', 'Letrozole is indicated to treat postmenopausal women with hormone receptor (HR) positive early breast cancer, postmenopausal women with early breast cancer who have periviously been treated with tamoxifen, and postmenopausal women with HR+ or unknown advanced breast cancer.[L11623] Letrozole, given with ribociclib, is indicated to treat pre, peri, and postmenopausal women with HR+ and human epidermal growth factor 2 (HER2) negative advanced or metastatic breast cancer.[L11626]', '6224001616082', '', 37344, '2024-12-04', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
